  "title": "SENIOR ACCOUNTS EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Perform general bookkeeping and full set of accounting functions - handle daily operational AP/AR tasks including invoicing, payment, receipts etc.</li><li>Perform monthly reconciliation and reports</li><li>Debts collections - Contact customer to ensure that their payments are made on time</li><li>GST filing</li><li>Prepare monthly sales commission and checking of incentives.</li><li>Handle any other ad-hoc hoc assignments and projects as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Reqirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Meticulous and organized</li><li>Possess positive learning attitude & a good team player</li><li>Pro-active and able to multi-task and work independently within deadline</li><li>Knowledge of \"XERO\" Software will be advantage</li><li>With at least 2 years accounting experience will be advantage</li></ul>",
